Comfyroll Workflow Templates
https://https://civitai.com/models/59806

This template can be used with any model.

On first use:
- select models and VAE
- select a default LoRA in each Load LoRA node
- select upscale models
- select ControlNet model
- add an image in each of the Load Images nodes (purple nodes)
- add a default image batch in the Load Image Batch node
- save a copy to use as a template

Tips:
- Example noise masks can be found in the Comfyroll Workflow Templates download
- Notes can be opened by clicking on the dots in the title bars (green nodes)
- Each optional component can be bypassed using logic switches (red nodes)
- The default setting for all logic switches is OFF (1)
